Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.51,0:00:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first sound, what was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.36,0:00:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That first sound of yours…
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.21,0:00:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because to me, it’s like this
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.65,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that’s why now, I’m happy
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first word, what was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.56,0:00:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That first word of yours
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.41,0:00:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I cannot speak words
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.60,0:00:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just like this, I sing on
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.96,0:01:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If at last days go by, years go by
Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.30,0:01:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If even the world loses its color
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.57,0:01:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I have the light you gave me
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.44,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter when, I shall sing
Dialogue: 5,0:01:23.34,0:01:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color of the sky, the smell of the wind
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.25,0:01:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of the ocean, even your voice
Dialogue: 5,0:01:32.93,0:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know none of them, but my song
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.86,0:01:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My song I will sing, just lifting my voice
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.64,0:01:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it could carry some message to you
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.84,0:01:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter when, no matter how long
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.24,0:01:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t change, I’ll stay how I was then
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.45,0:02:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I was at the First Sound…
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.34,0:02:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first sound, did you have it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.15,0:02:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That first sound of yours…
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.85,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do new songs, or the sounds of the city
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.80,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make you feel excited?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.61,0:02:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first word, did you have it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.37,0:02:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That first word of yours
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.16,0:02:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up without being said, those unsaid
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.98,0:03:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,words make me feel a little lonely
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.75,0:03:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If at last days go by, years go by
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.15,0:03:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and old burdens, too, pile up
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.41,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things you don’t want to lose
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of them all
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.31,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flow of time, the pain of scars
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.06,0:03:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of love, even your voice
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.76,0:03:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know none of them, but songs
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.63,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Songs I can sing, so please listen
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.47,0:03:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If perhaps you wish for it
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.65,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter when, no matter how long
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.02,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t change, I’ll stay how I was then
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.20,0:04:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I was at the First Sound…
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.16,0:04:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color of the sky, the smell of the wind
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.09,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of the ocean, even my song
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won’t change, they’ll stay how they were then
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.99,0:04:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they were at the First Sound…
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.76,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first sound, did I become it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.59,0:04:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That first sound of yours
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.33,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where in the world, I will sing
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.81,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,each and every First Sound...
